@startuml sequence_high_level
title High-Level Sequence Diagram - Parking Management and Guidance System

actor "Driver/User" as User
actor Admin

participant "Parking Management and Guidance System" as System
participant "Sensor/Camera System" as Sensor
participant "Payment Gateway" as Payment

User -> System: Check availability
System -> Sensor: Request live parking data
Sensor --> System: Availability and entry/exit updates
System --> User: Show available spaces

alt Space available
  User -> System: Reserve selected spot
  System --> User: Confirm reservation
  User -> System: Request route guidance
  System --> User: Display route to reserved spot

  User -> System: Checkout and pay fee
  System -> Payment: Process payment
  Payment --> System: Payment result
  System --> User: Payment confirmation
else Parking full
  System --> User: Display parking full message
end

Admin -> System: View occupancy
System --> Admin: Show data

Admin -> System: Manage parking spaces and pricing
System --> Admin: Confirm updates
@enduml
